Physician Telemedicine App Features

Everything physicians need to virtualize their services. Making the transition from in-person care to remote healthcare delivery a seamless experience for healthcare professionals.

High quality video conferencing

Remote enablement with high-quality, secure, face to face video communication to help you better serve your patients

Secure in-app messaging

Exchange end-to-end encrypted, secure, HIPAA compliant text based messages with the patients before, during or after an appointment.

Easy integration with other medical software

Develop a telemedicine app that integrates existing health IT systems like EHR and billing software, streamlining the workflow and boosting interoperability for your practice

Provider approved appointment scheduling

Optimum appointment scheduling process where the patients can choose the slots available and physicians can approve the same through the platform admin.

Patient Telemedicine App Features

Maximise patient satisfaction when delivering virtual care. A robust app guaranteed to deliver an exceptional patient experience while creating a strong brand identity for your practice.

Easy Search through Doctor Profiles

Advanced filters to facilitate patients finding the doctor they need. Sort through on the basis of reviews and ratings to help find the best match.

Sort through available slots and schedule appointments

Empower the patients to skim through the available slots and choose one that fits their schedule. Complete transparency into the scheduling process.

HIPAA Compliant physician consultations

Give patients access to convenient health consultations with due stress on privacy and data security.

Dedicated patient portal for interoperability

Enable patients to get a birds eye view of their medical history through access to historical data and clinical documentation.
